response.original_title: The Evolution of Ibiza: Can the White Isle retain its legendary magic?
response.overview: This feature-length documentary looks back at the history of the island’s party scene from hippy hangout to becoming the world’s no. 1 clubbing destination, and asks, “how did it happen?”.  We talk to DJs, club promotors, officials and locals to discuss what Ibiza’s future could look like.  We hope you enjoy our journey exploring the evolution of Ibiza’s club scene.
response.title: The Evolution of Ibiza: Can the White Isle retain its legendary magic?
